&lt;p&gt;You’ve been in sales 3–5 years, you live in Salesforce and Outreach, and you’re not just chasing deals—you’re building pipelines, handling objections, and consistently beating quota.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Close business.&lt;/strong&gt; Own the full sales cycle and bring vintage buyers and sellers onto Alt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
