&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are a builder.&lt;/strong&gt; You’re not here to maintain—you&#39;re here to help define the modern marketplace for vintage cards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Live for the history.&lt;/strong&gt; You can debate ‘52 Mantle centering, know the pop counts on key rookies, or geek out over Goudey, T206s, and Fleer Jordans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Want your passion to be your career.&lt;/strong&gt; Talking cards, advising collectors, and connecting people to the right opportunities is your dream job.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are coachable and curious.&lt;/strong&gt; Even if you don’t know every set or nuance, you’re eager to learn and humble enough to take feedback.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
