&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;alt.xyz&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Alt&lt;/a&gt; is unlocking the value of alternative assets, starting with the $5 B trading-card market. We let collectors buy, sell, vault, and finance their cards in one place and we are backed by leaders at Stripe, Coinbase, Seven Seven Six, and pro athletes like Tom Brady and Giannis Antetokounmpo. Our next frontier is real-time pricing at scale—the Alt Value that powers every trade, loan, and product on the platform.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Are Looking For&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
