&lt;li&gt;Are deeply curious about how value is assigned to unique, non-traditional, and conventionally “illiquid” asset classes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are a hands-on individual contributor who thrives in a zero-to-one startup environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are a product-minded builder who wants to see their work deployed in a user-facing production application.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
